    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is the game about:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wake up in a strange place surrounded only by white creepy hallways and lots of strange buttons. A hand reaches out from the wall to provide you with weird information. The buttons seem to be the key to your escape, observe carefully and remember what you see, with the buttons helping you open the way to the front. Beware, there may be anomalies in the hallways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301100/extras/82e36f28ab950801e97dea7c5fa13da7.avif?t=1736218152\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301100/extras_big/82e36f28ab950801e97dea7c5fa13da7.avif?t=1736218152 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple button puzzles challenge your wit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ingenious game design, enter the next door or loop endlessly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strange phenomena in the hallway add surprise to your puzzle-solving.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301100/extras/b05a98a8d37d9add27a2bec7ac310e59.poster.avif?t=1736218152\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301100/extras/b05a98a8d37d9add27a2bec7ac310e59.webm?t=1736218152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301100/extras/b05a98a8d37d9add27a2bec7ac310e59.mp4?t=1736218152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game is created by <strong>@LittleMaru</strong> with YAHAHA Horror Game Kit and YAHAHA assists the creator with packaging and publishing the game based on their request. Yahaha Horror Gamekit is tailored for imaginative creators and players who adore horror games, all without the need for any programming expertise.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301100/extras/c7d88622b1842da1e06acc07376cf056.avif?t=1736218152\" width=720 height=216 /></span></p>",
